    Finsbury Smaller Companies Trust.
    Foreign and Colonial Emerging Markets Investment Trust.
    Latin American Investment Trust.
    Gartmore Emerging Pacific Investment Trust.
    New Throgmorton Trust (1983).
    River and Mercantile Trust.
    M and G Second Dual Trust.
    M and G Recovery Investment Trust.
    Scottish Mortgage Trust.
    Morgan Grenfell Equity Income Trust.
    Alliance Trust.
