 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
Single premium
Pounds 10,000            pounds 31,071      pounds 96,463
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
As can be seen, where full commission is paid, Scottish Widows' charges
are significantly higher than the Lautro basis, yielding a lower
projected return. When the commission cost is stripped out, the reverse
is true on the monthly premium plan but not on the single premium
contract.
