business as well as airport retailing activities
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
'I support a free press. But in other countries they print facts
rather than innuendo.'
Mike Hoffman, chief executive, Thames Water
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
'The British press ought to be proud of what it has done (in bringing
to light the link between aid and trade)'
Andrew Neil, editor, Sunday Times
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
